data.description: Incredible space! Incredible UPDATES! Looking for a unique property with more than enough space and versatility to meet anyone’s needs? Look no further!! Boasting 5 bedrooms and 3 full bathrooms in total, with over 3,250 sq ft of space on 0.28 acre of land! Significant renovations in 2018 added a luxury one-bedroom apartment approximately 1000 sqft and a primary suite with about 600 sq ft of its own. The updates also included a new roof, new siding, new windows, new flooring, new HVAC and water heater, and updates to the bathroom and kitchen. It's all top quality selections too! This split-level home features a large living room upon entry, with a very spacious coat closet and already mounted TV! The premium simulated wood laminate floor is durable and attractive, and you will find it throughout the home. Adjacent is the dining room open to the kitchen with LED light fixtures, stainless steel appliances, 42” cabinets, soft-close drawers, pantry, and granite countertops, making this kitchen a culinary dream. The LG gas range with 5 burners and double oven makes family dinners and holidays a breeze. Down a few steps leads to the huge family room, equipped with a wood insert fireplace that has been serviced every year. The family room enjoys good natural light complimented by recessed lighting. Nearby is the shared laundry room, the utility room with access to the back patio, and another entrance from the driveway. The utility room houses the YORK High-efficiency gas furnace (2016), and AO Smith hot water heater (2018). From the main living room, steps up lead to the bedroom level. The first stop is a trendy shared bath with a rustic and iron pipework theme. It features a modular shower tub with a stainless steel luxury sprayer and attractive vanity, completed by exposed shelves. Continuing down the hall, there are three more bedrooms, all with lighted ceiling fans and generous closet space. An incredible highlight of this home is the glamorous primary bedroom, continuing the western rustic theme throughout. Sliding barn doors lead you into the massive 12x12 walk-in closet with built-in adjustable shelving. Just before entering the luxurious en-suite bath, you’ll find yet another sitting area, perfect for nighttime reading. The ensuite bath has unique features such as a dual vanity with a slate top, Edison glass pipe lighting, a soaking tub with spray handle, and a large walk-in shower with a pebble bottom and stone tile walls. Within the master suite is a bonus room that can serve as an at-home office, nursery, or sitting area. Travel outside to the backyard to find your own private oasis. The first section consists of an al fresco dining area, pergola, and porch swing. While the separate fenced portion extends over a vast majority of the lot, housing the playset, a garden area, and storage shed, and room to play! Last, is the additional one-bedroom luxury apartment with private entrance. It starts with an exquisite kitchen with 42” shaker and glass front cabinets, soft-close drawers, electric range and oven, stainless steel appliances, ample cabinet space, and an area for a small dining table. The natural light from the continuous wall of windows brings cheer and productivity. The open floor plan flows into the living room. From there, it leads you down a short hallway to the bedroom and separate large walk-in closet. The roomy and well-designed full bathroom has a large walk-in shower, luxury tile flooring, and sizable vanity. The apartment has a separate fenced-in concrete patio accessible from the driveway that also enters the apartment. Conveniently located just off of Rte 141 and RTE 2 (Kirkwood Highway), near Prices corner, minutes from the new Wegmans and access to everything you need. Near parks, restaurants, nightlife, and more, this home has everything you’re looking for! OFFER DEADLINE End of day Tuesday. April 23, 11:59 PM.
